'''德克蘭·約翰'''（{{lang-en|'''Declan John'''}}；{{bd|1995年|6月30日}}）是一位[[威爾士|威爾士]][[足球員|足球運動員]]。在場上的位置是後衛。現效力於[[英格蘭甲組足球聯賽|英甲]]球队[[博尔顿足球俱乐部|博尔顿]]。他也代表威爾士國家足球隊參賽<ref name="#1">{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23922411 |title=Bale wants to play for Wales in the World Cup qualifiers |date=2 September 2013 |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcast Corporation |accessdate=2 November 2013 |archive-date=2013-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016223213/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23922411 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==球會生涯==
德克蘭·約翰在[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|卡迪夫城]]接受足球訓練，2012年8月14日首次在職業比賽上場，該場比場是[[英格蘭足球聯賽盃|英格蘭足球聯賽盃]]第一輪作客對[[北安普顿足球俱乐部|北安普顿]]，以2-1戰敗出局<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19159869 |title=Northampton 1-2 Cardiff |publisher=BBC |date=2012-08-14 |accessdate=2012-08-17 |archive-date=2012-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120817003135/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19159869 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年1月5日[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]作客對[[马科斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|马科斯菲尔德]]，約翰第二次代表卡迪夫城上場，同樣又以2-1戰敗出局<ref>{{cite news|last1=Hughes|first1=Dewi|title=Macclesfield 2-1 Cardiff|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20877003|accessdate=19 December 2015|publisher=BBC Sport|date=3 January 2013|archive-date=2016-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160120104048/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20877003|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

德克蘭·約翰的聯賽首秀是2013年8月17日以2-0不敵[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|西汉姆联]]，這亦是他首場英超比賽。12月他與球會簽下長約至2018年<ref>{{cite news |title=Cardiff City and Wales defender Declan John agrees new contract |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/25197093 |work=BBC Sport |date=3 December 2015 |accessdate=3 December 2015 |archive-date=2016-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160919123136/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/25197093 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[2013–14賽季英格蘭超級聯賽|13/14球季]]，他共在聯賽上場20次，大多是替補在下半場入替，而球隊最終亦降回英冠聯賽<ref name=barns/>。

新球季新教練，[[拉塞尔·斯来德|拉塞尔·斯来德]]不起用約翰，並在2015年3月把他外借到[[巴恩斯利足球俱乐部|班士利]]至季末，期間共上場9次<ref name=barns>{{cite news|title=Barnsley sign Declan John on loan from Cardiff City|url=http://www.barnsleyfc.co.uk/news/article/barnsley-sign-declan-john-on-loan-from-cardiff-city-2318346.aspx|accessdate=19 December 2015|publisher=Barnsley F.C.|date=6 March 2015|archive-date=2016-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160529123030/http://www.barnsleyfc.co.uk/news/article/barnsley-sign-declan-john-on-loan-from-cardiff-city-2318346.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。外借結束後回到卡城，約翰在15/16球季上半季只在聯賽上場一次而已，於是2016年2月被外借到英甲球會[[切斯特菲尔德足球俱乐部|切斯特菲尔德]].<ref>{{cite news |title=Jordan Slew and Declan John: Chesterfield sign duo |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/35606193 |work=BBC Sport |date=18 February 2016 |accessdate=18 February 2016 |archive-date=2017-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170106175957/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/35606193 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，上場6次後在4月14日被召回至母會<ref>{{cite news |title=More to come from Declan John at Chesterfield, says Danny Wilson |url=http://www.derbyshiretimes.co.uk/sport/football/chesterfield-fc/more-to-come-from-declan-john-at-chesterfield-says-danny-wilson-1-7751133 |work=Derbyshire Times |date=25 February 2016 |accessdate=25 February 2016 |archive-date=2017-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170122153944/http://www.derbyshiretimes.co.uk/sport/football/chesterfield-fc/more-to-come-from-declan-john-at-chesterfield-says-danny-wilson-1-7751133 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Cardiff City recall Declan John as 'precaution' ahead of play-off run in |url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/cardiff-city-recall-declan-john-11185263 |work=Wales Online |date=14 April 2016 |accessdate=14 April 2016 |archive-date=2017-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170122153426/http://www.walesonline.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/cardiff-city-recall-declan-john-11185263 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2016/17球季揭幕日，德克蘭·約翰以先發身份上場對[[伯明翰足球會|伯明翰城]]，以0-0悶和完場，賽後他當選為全場最佳球員<ref>{{cite news |title=Birmingham City 0–0 Cardiff City |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/36929866 |work=BBC Sport |date=6 August 2016 |accessdate=6 August 2016 |archive-date=2017-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170315050214/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/36929866 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==國家隊生涯==
德克蘭·約翰首次被[[威爾斯足球代表隊|威爾斯]]成年隊徵召是2013年9月舉行的[[2014年世界盃足球賽|2014年世界盃足球賽]]資格賽<ref name="#1"/>，該兩場比賽他均是未有上場的替補員<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23964942 |title=Macedonia 2-1 Wales |date=6 September 2013 |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcast Corporation |accessdate=2 November 2013 |archive-date=2015-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150726185223/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23964942 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/24011041 |title=Wales 0-3 Serbia |date=10 September 2013 |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcast Corporation |accessdate=2 November 2013 |archive-date=2015-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151203103822/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/24011041 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。10月份對馬其頓和比利時的比賽亦同樣被徵召上成年隊<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/24381327 |title=Gareth Bale withdraws from Wales squad with thigh injury |date=3 October 2013 |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcast Corporation |accessdate=2 November 2013 |archive-date=2014-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140807071531/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/24381327 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並在10月11日主場1-0擊敗馬其頓的賽事中首次為威爾斯上場並踢滿90分鐘，最終以1-0全取3分<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/24393705 |title=Wales 1-0 Macedonia |date=11 October 2013 |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcast Corporation |accessdate=2 November 2013 |archive-date=2013-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131207070245/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/24393705 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

